A vintage 1950s horror movie poster style illustration showing a massive, menacing server tower rising like a monster from a chaotic pit of tangled cables and smoking circuit boards, casting an ominous shadow over tiny terrified IT workers in retro clothing who are scrambling away with their tools, the scene bathed in dramatic red and orange lighting with billowing smoke clouds, the server covered in blinking warning lights and sparking electrical arcs, rendered with classic mid-century print textures and halftone dot patterns.
